              "id": "S2_PART1_A_Q2_solution_2",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "2.\na) Three aspects of ethics: 1- the obligation to be honest and lawful in ones activities. 2- to act in conformity with the spirit of fair competition 3- the payment of one's taxes / and the necessity to treat one's employees with fairness.\nb) Ethics keeps the balance of economy. Any mistake or wrongdoing disturbs its balance and penalizes its functioning.\nc) misbehaviours get punished severely."
